PRD — Nutritionist Platform (All EPICs 1–21)
Minimalistic LLM‑Optimized Version

EPIC 1 — User & Authentication System
User Stories
As a nutritionist, I want to create an account so I can access the platform.

As a user, I want to log in using email/password so I can securely access my data.

As a user, I want to reset my password so I can recover access.

As an admin, I want to manage user roles (Lite, Premium, Business) so I can control feature access.

As a business account owner, I want to add/remove team members so I can manage my clinic staff.

